<plot>A radio voice promises Mr. Lion, in the jungle, three square meals a day if he takes up residence in a cage in the Happy Zoo, in the Bronx, and Mr. Lion rushes right there but all he gets to eat are round vitamin pills, and he is not a happy cager. He escapes, is captured and is brought back, but he isn't hungry any longer, and the radio announcer is no longer around.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?435976</url></doc>
